title: UI Builder UDRs - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: The UI Builder agent contains a number of UDRs. In the UDR Internal Format Browser , a detailed view of the available UDRs and respective fields is displayed. To open the browser, click the Configuration menu and select the option APL Code , and then right-click in the editing area and select the option UDR Assistance... . This section contains the following subsections: General UI Builder UDRs UI Builder Component UDRs
